high_descs: Turn back and walk straight to reach the microwave oven

Turn back and walk straight and enter into the bathroom and reach the toilet
Cut the bread loaf which is kept on the toilet top
Little bit move towards the left side to reach the sink
Put the knife on the sink
Little bit move towards the right side to reach the cut bread slices on the toilet top
Take a bread slice from the cut bread
Turn left and walk out of the bathroom and walk straight to reach the microwave oven
Open the oven and put the bread piece inside the oven and after heating open the oven and take back the bread slice and close the oven
Little bit move towards the left side to reach the table
Put the bread slice on the table

Slice the bread on the back of the sofa.

Place the knife in the sink in the bathroom.
Turn to the bread on the back of the toilet.
Pick up a slice of bread from the middle.

Place the bread in the microwave, heat the bread, and take it out of the microwave.

Place the slice of bread on the dining table.

Pick up the knife from the microwave.

Put the knife in the sink.
